":"2018-07-03T13:35:44.000Z","msg":"今次哈比有用好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b6d727dd298317156b434051c719432d4993717f","tid":718204,"uid":3020,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-03T15:15:44.000Z","msg":"第2話 中文<br />\n<a href=\"https://tieba.baidu.com/p/5780515156?see_lz=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftieba.baidu.com%2Fp%2F5780515156%3Fsee_lz%3D1&d=R0syECZasz%2BGAEeQHIG%2BTl0Hwm5JNK6yt%2FgZtp%2B4HOw%3D&h=8be89e77\" target=\"_blank\">https://tieba.baidu.com/p/5780515156?see_lz=1</a>"},{"pid":"c87e8a88a9b58f8c0e02301a849bf44a61017844","tid":718204,"uid":91527,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"c4445138d201ee989361917d000c32e69e0120af","tid":718204,"uid":12025,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-03T13:17:40.000Z","msg":"點解佢畫唔返聖石小子個種質素既作品<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-03T23:51:25.000Z","msg":"到目前為止第2話都仲係幾好睇<br />\n聖石一開始都唔係咁好睇<br />\n係去到打殛克/開始講莉莎果時先至入戲玉<br />\n聖石點解好睇係因為佢有個好明顯既故事主軸<br />\n就係解開莉莎秘密同集齊聖石<br />\n成套野既伏筆同埋分支劇情都係圍繞住主線來走<br />\n所以你會覺得成套野係好完整<br />\n<br />\n妖尾因為係玩公會出任接任<br />\n每個篇章都好獨立好唔連貫<br />\n每個篇章都可有可無咁<br />\n主線劇情就好弱<br />\n<br />\n如果今次玩冒險者公會又係好似妖尾咁接任解任冇主線就真係GG<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bae439b52ae87bfd6e6797d514a7264f637e6c2f","tid":718204,"uid":3020,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-04T11:47:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/04/194712_d90625d81e53593d0c8cf3bc43ac0214.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F04%2F194712_d90625d81e53593d0c8cf3bc43ac0214.jpg&h=1bda966d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\